T1  - A duopoly theory of government money production: The 1930s and 1940s
AU  - Toma, Mark
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 15
IS  - 3
SP  - 363
EP  - 382
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/05/01/
